{"tid":1838572,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"湖北省啟動「重大突發公共衞生事件Ⅰ級響應」","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:07:10.000Z","uid":30647,"like":159,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"b82af3879847633d6b40b4cafdd53d968339ac64","tid":1838572,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"去到最大鑊嘅 I 級， I級等同於發生或者核事故和突發放射事故 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=======<br />\n湖北省新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指揮部，今日中午發佈通告，啟動湖北省「重大突發公共衞生事件Ⅰ級響應」。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《國家突發公共事件總體應急預案》的規定，應急預案分為自然災害、事故災難、公共衞生事件、社會安全事件等4類。而該機制將突發事件按照嚴重程度由低到高分為Ⅳ級（一般）、Ⅲ級（較大）、Ⅱ級（重大）、Ⅰ級（特別重大）等4個級別。而<span style=\"color: red;\">I級等同於發生或者核事故和突發放射事故</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200124/4VF3YYH6YYLFSRJSJRCPI4FZHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200124%2F4VF3YYH6YYLFSRJSJRCPI4FZHU%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=dd76effa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200124%2F4VF3YYH6YYLFSRJSJRCPI4FZHU%2F&h=f1c4f472\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200124/4VF3YYH6YYLFSRJSJRCPI4FZHU/</a>"},{"pid":"0fae73904ed5e6d7ce90b74aee209e80d48a0193","tid":1838572,"uid":185092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec2bee05dfe9d8e46c55447080923ca3573d1dc","tid":1838572,"uid":3776,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"支爆支爆"},{"pid":"919a3e89283fff5082e9f67b5c7512b96a0b1fbc","tid":1838572,"uid":235277,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"2020 支那大爆炸"},{"pid":"48ff